與自由地區選舉無關；<br />\n<br />\n第三，香港人用盡時間金錢，部分義士甚至付出前途生命，並且與香港各界合作是次運動。我們不希望自由地區再次有人大搞分化，借刀拿選票以至搞臺灣獨立，消費香港人；<br />\n<br />\n第四，聯署黨員再一次聲明，我們支持黨中央決策，也支持總統候選人。不割蓆，不分化。<br />\n<br />\n最後，聯署香港黨員重申，譴責共匪出動黑幫打巿民，無視香港巿民訴求。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n反共絕無妥協，奮鬥才能自由！<br />\n中華民國萬歲！<br />\n一羣愛香港的中國國民黨香港黨員<br />\n中華民國一百零八年七月三十日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zK2Nk9J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzK2Nk9J.jpg&h=58463e57&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:56:43.000Z","msg":"同志，其實出聲明前是否有知會黨支部?因為貿然出呢種聲明，本意係好，但會俾綠營口實，對明年選舉不利。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:54:58.000Z","msg":"國民黨青年團已發出聲明表能支持香港人<br />\n我相信綠營會扮睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4nE0Nu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4nE0Nu.jpg&h=53c92ea9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33f28ef559002580f5e9938945c7f29b23533060","tid":1388382,"uid":60037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8997b6a38a91f5d2a9431d5d468562aa84d31f2e","tid":1388382,"uid":107405,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:59:47.000Z","msg":"以前既國民黨 有既係蔣經國呢d思路清晰 睇中共睇得透徹既政治家<br />\n仲有李登輝呢d背負理念 將自己染黑係人地陣營入面一步一步爬上KMT最高位再將佢地一舖清既陰謀家(非貶義)<br />\n<br />\n依家就只剩低一班貪圖自己發大財之輩 利用台灣未來當成自己工具黎揸搾壓金錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:56:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">蔣經國不人道刑求好多政治犯<br />\n佢嘅開放政策係因為受到當時美國卡特總統「人權外交」嘅壓力<br />\n同埋蚛華冥蟈喺台灣，由頭到尾都只不過係美國嘅契弟。</span>"},{"pid":"9da2bb6db425cc11b400a3846e74da15e70f84f6","tid":1388382,"uid":258069,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"88c2fdfb4e83441a51f3750ee89e2af70f4d86cb","tid":1388382,"uid":60037,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:53:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">估唔到上連登都會睇到你地呢班冥國垃圾<br />\n屌你老母食屎啦中國國民黨</span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:00:12.000Z","msg":"分化撚死開<br />\n我哋啲人打生打死嘅時候，你知唔知？<br />\n入埋醫院搞到長期食藥，你知唔知？<br />\n連文宣都有我哋啲人幫手，你知唔知？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f829efa511f774a8f6a233b643e436f1dc9d48bd","tid":1388382,"uid":258069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:04:32.000Z","msg":"2017年9月<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cuEj0QU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcuEj0QU.png&h=75e3fd50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1MPTkQ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1MPTkQ3.png&h=572be257&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff8987ca9736c31080662dc7fff9c7430e8ed33b","tid":1388382,"uid":258069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:09:53.000Z","msg":"推到返台灣"},{"pid":"4847878e7eb1495720c1fd24cf1b8bb099c1609f","tid":1388382,"uid":11436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:12:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c34c781e0da3d17f0ba20f530e1e074833e494d","tid":1388382,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"022ffac4b08bb784f581ea88c1d89d099916aed5","tid":1388382,"uid":258069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7985c50fa75175a63fb001f5fcc67c327a6769b5","tid":1388382,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d088f876fb7483e4d6dfa0430cf916f93b9b007c","tid":1388382,"uid":258069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:02:06.000Z","msg":"首先 我哋係支持黨中決定 冇講過支持韓國魚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:06:23.000Z","msg":"你篇聲明寫支持kmt總統候選人喎<br />\n<br />\n咁賣國魚係咩來嫁"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:21:34.000Z","msg":"我哋係支持黨中央，唔係支持條魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"第四，聯署黨員再一次聲明，我們支持黨中央決策，也<span style=\"color: red;\">支持總統候選人</span>。不割蓆，不分化。<br />\n<br />\n請問你紅色字代表緊乜"},{"pid":"ef9fe47a04a74657b17adc5e6dc7243d85a6949d",